        </item>
        <item>
            <title>电动车品牌 Polestar 专属手机，现身 Google Play 支援名单推出在望</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/10/polestar-phone-emerges-in-google-play-supported-devices-list/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=polestar-phone-emerges-in-google-play-supported-devices-list</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/10/polestar-phone-emerges-in-google-play-supported-devices-list/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 05:00:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[polestar]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Polestar Phone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[魅族]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1219748</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>电动车厂商 Polestar 于去年 11 月，在他们的品牌活动日上透露有意推出 Polestar Phone 智能手机，并且公开了少量手机设计的照片。事隔数月，Polestar Phone 被发现在 Google Play 的支援名单中，跟其他中国品牌魅族的手机并列。</p><p><span id="more-1219748"></span></p><p>Polestar Phone 与众多魅族手机一同出现于名单，原因相信是这款手机将会由魅族负责代工生产。自从 2017 年开始，Polestar 就隶属吉利汽车集团旗下，而魅族则在 2022 年被吉利集团董事长李书福收购，并成为星纪魅族科技有限公司成员，故此两家公司关系相当密切，后者亦会参与开发 Polestar 在中国上市版本的车载系统。</p><p>有外国媒体相信 Polestar Phone 在 Google Play 支援名单出现，代表这款手机距离正式发表又近了一步。虽然 Polestar 的电动车在全球多国都有发售，但据说采用旗舰级规格的 Polestar Phone，有可能只会在中国市场推出，以配合当地发售的车款并未采用国际版预载的 Android Automotive 系统。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_59155"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Y_r-lJhVy_4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/polestar_phone_emerges_in_google_play_supported_devices_list-news-61523.php">gsmarena</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/03/volvo-cars-stop-funding-polestar/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Volvo 宣布停止向 Polestar 注资　责任将会转交吉利汽车</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/polestar-cut-around-450-jobs-globally/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Polestar 全球裁员 15%　市场形势不乐观导致</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/11/polestar-phone-design-leaked/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">加强车主使用体验   Polestar Phone 机身设计流出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/10/polestar-phone-emerges-in-google-play-supported-devices-list/mobile-phone/">电动车品牌 Polestar 专属手机，现身 Google Play 支援名单推出在望</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
